{"tid":931954,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"摩連奴：我的工作不可思議，排在很多潛力比曼聯大的球隊之前","createTime":"2018-12-07T11:25:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-08T08:53:11.000Z","uid":124292,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"46c4e1e8d0a1fc1e0af532fa80d0335be9feab0c","tid":931954,"uid":124292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T11:25:12.000Z","msg":"曼聯將在本週末迎來主場對陣富咸的英超聯賽，他在賽前記者會上回答提問。<br />\n<br />\n如果這場沒贏，那說明了什麼？<br />\n<br />\n「我想積極一點，去想我們能贏下來。但如果我們沒贏，我們會稱贊那些配得上稱贊的球員，比賽不會是11對0的樣子，是11對11。<strong>我再說一遍，排名、積分有時不能多少說明球隊和英超歷史上最重要的兩位教練之一的真實潛力。</strong>在我看來，他們有潛力來這裡和我們踢一場非常困難的比賽。<br />\n<br />\n你能解釋你為何將上賽季排名第二視為你最大的成就之一嗎？<br />\n<br />\n「我在說一支可能排名第十的球隊和一位感覺像冠軍的教練，對吧？」<br />\n<br />\n「如果對大衛、賓尼迪斯、雲尼亞里說他們會排名第十，他們的感覺會像一位冠軍。我做了不可思議的工作，我排在很多潛力比我的球隊大的球隊前面，就這麼簡單。」"},{"pid":"7071b490cfc63138e63f6bbdd5a9b123ca0742ef","tid":931954,"uid":124292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T11:26:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.manchestereveningnews.co.uk/sport/football/man-utd-mourinho-conference-live-15518716\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.manchestereveningnews.co.uk%2Fsport%2Ffootball%2Fman-utd-mourinho-conference-live-15518716&d=OG2FKvExQ3NIMvp287CNa%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=1446b878\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.manchestereveningnews.co.uk/sport/football/man-utd-mourinho-conference-live-15518716</a>"},{"pid":"ac6bde2034c3b5a5ede01203b4b25ce2767c2440","tid":931954,"uid":30768,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T11:32:50.000Z","msg":"真係痴咗線"},{"pid":"d3b4b4f0f1938b8bfe0e05fb8bdb7cb8ea94ad4c","tid":931954,"uid":132082,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T12:03:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c9b7ca953125f0ec60acd5dbc456ccddf212753a","tid":931954,"uid":14977,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T12:05:43.000Z","msg":"其他隊隊都有錢買人，得daddy限米煮限飯，算係咁啦"},{"pid":"4c215fee020d5f6d1616cd0109e